<section id="support-main" class="support page navigable text">
  <section class="container">
    <h6><a href="../support">&larr; Svbtle support</a></h6>
    <h1 class="">Uploading and using images</h1>

    <p>To add an image to an article, drag and drop it into the editor. Svbtle will automatically upload the image and paste the correct Markdown text into the editor.</p>

    <p>You can also paste embed <code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code> or JavaScript code from Twitter or YouTube into the editor.</p>

    <hr/>

    <p>If you need more help, send us an email: <a href="mailto:hello@svbtle.com?subject=Custom%20domain%20help" class="">hello@svbtle.com</a>.</p>

    <hr>

    <a href="../support" class="harsh tiny">Back to support</a>
  </section>
